        "description": "Qwen2.5 7B Instruct is a powerful language model designed for instruction-following tasks. It is based on the Qwen architecture and has been fine-tuned to excel at understanding and generating human-like responses to a wide range of prompts. With its 7 billion parameters, it strikes a balance between performance and resource efficiency, making it suitable for various applications such as chatbots, content generation, and more.",
